<c.white><c.mono_sans>of her voice</c.mono_sans></c.white>

727
00:25:07.923 --> 00:25:12.052  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>that she's not a monster</c.mono_sans></c.white>

728
00:25:07.923 --> 00:25:12.052  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>at all, but a child...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

729
00:25:12.052 --> 00:25:14.680  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>a little girl.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

730
00:25:14.680 --> 00:25:17.808  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Mr. Neelix, I...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

731
00:25:21.020 --> 00:25:25.941  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Her name was Palaxia.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

732
00:25:27.567 --> 00:25:31.529  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:63.33%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>We brought her back to Talax</c.mono_sans></c.white>

733
00:25:27.567 --> 00:25:31.529  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>with the other survivors.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

734
00:25:31.529 --> 00:25:35.326  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Over the next few weeks,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

735
00:25:31.529 --> 00:25:35.326  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I stayed at her bedside</c.mono_sans></c.white>

736
00:25:35.326 --> 00:25:37.661  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:63.33%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and watched her wither away.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

737
00:25:41.790 --> 00:25:45.252  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Those are consequences,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

738
00:25:41.790 --> 00:25:45.252  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:30.95%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Dr. Jetrel.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

739
00:25:50.216 --> 00:25:51.967  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>There is no way</c.mono_sans></c.white>

740
00:25:51.967 --> 00:25:56.305  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I can ever apologize</c.mono_sans></c.white>

741
00:25:51.967 --> 00:25:56.305  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to you, Mr. Neelix.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

742
00:25:57.515 --> 00:26:00.226  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:63.33%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That's why I have not tried.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

743
00:26:02.186 --> 00:26:06.273  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Did you ever think that</c.mono_sans></c.white>

744
00:26:02.186 --> 00:26:06.273  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:59.52%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>maybe your wife was right?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

745
00:26:06.273 --> 00:26:09.193  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:67.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That you had become a monster?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

746
00:26:10.236 --> 00:26:11.404  position:46.19%,start  align:start size:17.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Yes.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

747
00:26:13.780 --> 00:26:15.615  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>The day we tested</c.mono_sans></c.white>

748
00:26:13.780 --> 00:26:15.615  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:32.86%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>the Cascade,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

749
00:26:15.615 --> 00:26:19.745  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>when I saw that</c.mono_sans></c.white>

750
00:26:15.615 --> 00:26:19.745  position:36.67%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>blinding light</c.mono_sans></c.white>

751
00:26:19.745 --> 00:26:21.914  position:36.67%,start  align:start size:34.76%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>brighter than</c.mono_sans></c.white>

752
00:26:19.745 --> 00:26:21.914  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>a thousand suns...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

753
00:26:23.916 --> 00:26:29.380  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I knew at that moment</c.mono_sans></c.white>

754
00:26:23.916 --> 00:26:29.380  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:59.52%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>exactly what I had become.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

755
00:26:29.380 --> 00:26:33.426  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I hope you have to live</c.mono_sans></c.white>

756
00:26:29.380 --> 00:26:33.426  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>with that a very long time.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

757
00:26:33.426 --> 00:26:38.264  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'm afraid you will not</c.mono_sans></c.white>

758
00:26:33.426 --> 00:26:38.264  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:59.52%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>get your wish, Mr. Neelix.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

759
00:26:38.264 --> 00:26:40.140  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And why is that?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

760
00:26:40.140 --> 00:26:42.184  position:46.19%,start  align:start size:27.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>( sighs )</c.mono_sans></c.white>

761
00:26:42.184 --> 00:26:44.270  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I have advanced metremia.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

762
00:26:44.270 --> 00:26:47.106  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I will be dead</c.mono_sans></c.white>

763
00:26:44.270 --> 00:26:47.106  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
