<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'm no coward.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

770
00:27:06.375 --> 00:27:07.834  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That's not what I've heard.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

771
00:27:07.834 --> 00:27:09.669  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Wait, what are you doing?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

772
00:27:07.834 --> 00:27:09.669  position:36.67%,start  align:start size:34.76%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>It's my turn.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

773
