<c.white><c.mono_sans>You were afraid!</c.mono_sans></c.white>

779
00:27:18.971 --> 00:27:21.932  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:15.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No!</c.mono_sans></c.white>

