<c.white><c.mono_sans>Why weren't you here to help us?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

786
00:27:31.233 --> 00:27:32.359  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:27.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>( gasps )</c.mono_sans></c.white>

787
00:27:36.614 --> 00:27:38.532  position:46.19%,start  align:start size:17.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You!</c.mono_sans></c.white>

788
00:27:38.532 --> 00:27:40.326  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You did this, butcher!</c.mono_sans></c.white>

789
00:27:44.330 --> 00:27:46.790  position:42.38%,start  align:start size:25.24%  line:79.29% 
