00:27:44.330 --> 00:27:46.790  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<i><c.white><c.mono_sans>Bridge to Neelix.</c.mono_sans></c.white></i>

791
00:27:52.212 --> 00:27:53.964  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>H-Here, Captain.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

792
00:27:53.964 --> 00:27:56.383  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:79.29% 
<i><c.white><c.mono_sans>Neelix, I thought</c.mono_sans></c.white></i>

793
00:27:53.964 --> 00:27:56.383  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:84.62% 
<i><c.white><c.mono_sans>you'd like to know.</c.mono_sans></c.white></i>

794
