<i><c.white><c.mono_sans>We're approaching Rinax.</c.mono_sans></c.white></i>

795
00:28:02.306 --> 00:28:03.474  position:42.38%,start  align:start size:23.33%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Neelix?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

