798
00:28:10.523 --> 00:28:12.525  position:42.38%,start  align:start size:25.24%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Entering</c.mono_sans></c.white>

799
00:28:10.523 --> 00:28:12.525  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>synchronous orbit, Captain.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

800
00:28:12.525 --> 00:28:14.360  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>( door opening )</c.mono_sans></c.white>

801
00:28:23.827 --> 00:28:27.540  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Hard to believe</c.mono_sans></c.white>

