00:28:23.827 --> 00:28:27.540  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>that on clear nights</c.mono_sans></c.white>

803
00:28:27.540 --> 00:28:28.957  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:63.33%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>you could look up from Talax</c.mono_sans></c.white>

804
00:28:28.957 --> 00:28:32.169  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:65.24%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and see the shimmering lights</c.mono_sans></c.white>

805
00:28:28.957 --> 00:28:32.169  position:36.67%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>of the colony.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

806
00:28:34.421 --> 00:28:37.591  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>The night of the Cascade,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

807
00:28:37.591 --> 00:28:41.261  position:36.67%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>a bright flash</c.mono_sans></c.white>

808
00:28:37.591 --> 00:28:41.261  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>cut across the sky--</c.mono_sans></c.white>

809
00:28:41.261 --> 00:28:44.390  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>so blinding that people</c.mono_sans></c.white>

810
00:28:44.390 --> 00:28:45.849  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>threw themselves</c.mono_sans></c.white>

811
00:28:44.390 --> 00:28:45.849  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to the ground...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

812
00:28:48.185 --> 00:28:52.314  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and everything stopped</c.mono_sans></c.white>

813
00:28:48.185 --> 00:28:52.314  position:25.24%,start  align:start size:59.52%  line:84.62% 
