814
00:28:53.357 --> 00:28:54.941  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Then we all looked up</c.mono_sans></c.white>

815
00:28:54.941 --> 00:28:59.697  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to see where the flash</c.mono_sans></c.white>

816
00:28:54.941 --> 00:28:59.697  position:36.67%,start  align:start size:36.67%  line:84.62% 
