<c.white><c.mono_sans>but the sky seemed oddly empty.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

818
00:29:06.119 --> 00:29:08.163  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>It took most of us</c.mono_sans></c.white>

819
00:29:06.119 --> 00:29:08.163  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:84.62% 
