<c.white><c.mono_sans>it was because Rinax was...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

821
00:29:11.791 --> 00:29:13.669  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:19.52%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>gone.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

822
00:29:13.669 --> 00:29:15.837  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Of course, the moon</c.mono_sans></c.white>

823
