<c.white><c.mono_sans>was still there.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

824
00:29:15.837 --> 00:29:19.049  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:69.05%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>We just couldn't see it because</c.mono_sans></c.white>

825
00:29:15.837 --> 00:29:19.049  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>of that Metreon cloud.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

826
00:29:19.049 --> 00:29:21.427  position:42.38%,start  align:start size:23.33%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>TORRES:</c.mono_sans></c.white>

827
00:29:19.049 --> 00:29:21.427  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:84.62% 
<i><c.white><c.mono_sans>Engineering to Bridge.</c.mono_sans></c.white></i>

828
00:29:21.427 --> 00:29:24.263  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:30.95%  line:73.96% 
<i><c.white><c.mono_sans>We're ready</c.mono_sans></c.white></i>

